text: The Jammu and Kashmir women's cricket team is an Indian domestic cricket team representing the Indian state of Jammu and Kashmir. The team has represented the state in Senior women’s one day league (List A) and Senior women's T20 league. == See also == * Sports in Jammu and Kashmir * Jammu and Kashmir men's cricket team ==References== Category:Women's cricket teams in India
title: Jammu and Kashmir women's cricket team
